Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.43,0:15:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦克死了  拉罗也死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mike's in the ground. Lalo's in the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必为了我而犹豫不决\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You don't have to hold back on my account.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们只能处死我一次  所以你尽管去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They can only hang me once. So-- So go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全说出来  自我惩罚吧  看对你有什么好处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Spill your guts! Put on your hair shirt, see what it gets you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.70,0:15:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金  我们为什么说起自首\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kim, why are we even talking about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.28,0:15:37.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们都很聪明  不会无缘无故毁掉自己人生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're both too smart to throw our lives away for no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.27,0:15:38.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.46,0:15:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just... I only wanted to...
