Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.08,0:20:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}假造他可卡因成瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:06.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}塞拉曼加进入了我们家...  头部中枪  霍华德立即死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.81,0:21:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}我按照指示  开车去弗林家\N厄门绍特毁灭证据...\N...伪装成自杀...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,霍华德是被人杀害的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Howard was murdered?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.74,0:21:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.44,0:21:50.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不该在那时出现在那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the wrong place at the wrong time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的尸体在哪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where's his body?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.59,0:22:12.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警方呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.00,0:22:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会再搜寻吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will they search again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They'll search.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.72,0:22:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得他们应该找不到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't think they'll find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.75,0:22:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢丽尔  他...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cheryl, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.04,0:22:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都发生在一瞬间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It-- it all happened in an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.15,0:22:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他没有受苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he didn't-- he didn't suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.17,0:22:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他没有受苦"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"He didn't suffer."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.24,0:22:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你俩编出的谎言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The lies you two made up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.92,0:22:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们描绘出的那个他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The picture you painted.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在完全是那个人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all he is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.08,0:23:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人只记得那样的他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That's all anybody remembers.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.04,0:23:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想改变现状\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I want to change that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来会怎么样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happens now?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:12.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会受审吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will you be tried?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.26,0:23:14.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会坐牢吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Will you go to jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.08,0:23:17.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.70,0:23:20.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是律师  对吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a lawyer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.23,0:23:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是个了不起的律师  霍华德说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're a-- A great one, Howard said!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.82,0:23:25.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How could you not know?
