Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.61,0:23:35.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是否起诉要看地检官\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's up to the district attorney whether to prosecute.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她可能不会起诉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And she may not.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.29,0:23:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why?
