Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.20,0:34:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没什么好看的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing to see here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.25,0:34:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Move on.
